WEBVTT

00:03:29.301 --> 00:03:33.478
Štoviše, vitezovi u "Ekskaliburu"
svuda nose svoje oklope.

00:03:33.502 --> 00:03:37.025
Stalno -- nose ih za večerom,
u krevetu.

00:03:37.049 --> 00:03:38.100
(Smijeh)

00:03:38.124 --> 00:03:39.994
Pomislio sam, "Zar mi čitaju misli?

00:03:40.018 --> 00:03:42.486
I ja želim stalno nositi zaštitni oklop!"

00:03:42.510 --> 00:03:43.525
(Smijeh)

00:03:43.549 --> 00:03:45.748
Tako sam se vratio
svome najdražem materijalu,

00:03:45.772 --> 00:03:47.321
slamka spasa kod rukotvorina

00:03:47.345 --> 00:03:48.765
rebrasti karton,

00:03:48.789 --> 00:03:51.651
i napravio sam sebi oklopno odijelo,

00:03:51.675 --> 00:03:55.120
upotpunjeno štitovima za vrat
i bijelim konjem.

00:03:55.144 --> 00:03:56.410
Sad kad sam ga previše nahvalio

00:03:56.434 --> 00:03:58.460
evo slika oklopa koji sam napravio.

00:03:58.484 --> 00:03:59.825
(Smijeh)

00:03:59.849 --> 00:04:02.299
(Aplauz)